{"tid":767814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好事成雙] 中國最大玉米貿易商吉林糧食 驚傳已破產","createTime":"2018-08-05T00:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T04:47:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c64e1a1df638f5b561a5a2ce752624c6806fab98","tid":767814,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"中國最大玉米貿易商吉林糧食 驚傳已破產<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2509490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2509490&d=%2FyshlLpn4ccxj6cNBwbS8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1f8f8beb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2509490&h=238d2a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2509490</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕就在中國在7月底宣布全面徹查全國糧倉後，吉林大型國企、中國最大玉米貿易商吉林糧食集團，竟然驚傳已經破產遭到清算。<br />\n<br />\n根據《新京報》報導，吉林省長春市中級人民法院近日發佈民事裁定書，吉林糧食集團外貿公司興華糧庫，已無法清償到期債務且明顯缺乏清償能力，裁定受理該公司的破產重整申請。<br />\n<br />\n報導也發現，進入8月以來，包含興華糧庫在內的多家吉林糧食集團子公司，都在申請破產重整。<br />\n<br />\n但實際上，根據報導，早在興華糧庫之前，母公司吉林糧食集團就已經破產。根據法院文件，吉林糧食在2013到2014年間，向外借款5400萬人民幣，卻因無法如期償還，被債權人告到法院要求進行破產清算，法院也在今年5月向公司提出通知，而吉林糧食也已明確表示同意進行破產清算。<br />\n<br />\n吉林糧食對於破產消息並沒有做出回應，但根據公司提出的破產報告，吉林糧食目前負債率超過100%，並仍然拖欠旗下27名員工薪資、社保費用和醫療保險等費用。<br />\n<br />\n吉林糧食集團在1996年正式成立，是中國農業產業化的重點企業，也是極少數擁有糧食進出口經營權的企業，也是中國最大的玉米貿易商。但吉林糧食近年卻深陷貪腐案，基層糧庫裡出現不少私設「小金庫」，個別幹部也與親屬藉由企業牟取私利。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，吉林糧食黨委書記、董事長孟久祥也因為規避組織調查等嚴重違紀問題，遭到開除黨籍、追繳違紀所得，並移送法辦。"},{"pid":"1558ae304be2b8061fdf46a2e87b0ec191850747","tid":767814,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"破完大豆商，輪到粟米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下一個農產品會係咩？"},{"pid":"63794f140c93f9ad970a5f6a0b1470a59f0cefbe","tid":767814,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"無啦無啦濕米都無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556d8c4439b491fa706a8e58f5088cc4bfe7da46","tid":767814,"uid":143967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"索性等爆煲由國家救"},{"pid":"a05c6391c4eec14cf7200d67ecde005c8bada920","tid":767814,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dbce0c01d333cb7e389c9e56ce58a976f37cda6","tid":767814,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"充公完又有錢可以比雜種大灑幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12081738d5633886143f06e0e0e59c87eb62d1f","tid":767814,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ac7b448078791bd411ffdc7e64aee9e8f0b39a","tid":767814,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:12:28.000Z","msg":"咁睇d內銀應該會仆街<br />\n<br />\n壞帳直線升"},{"pid":"61d3bd5f910ee1394b39d27f73076d560445f327","tid":767814,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"下一個係橙？"},{"pid":"84beed8a4638d16d177cbc34c8a4d0f28acd34cc","tid":767814,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c193fed5652b9425d632886a0bf5821785d9bd91","tid":767814,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"幾時變返做糧票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img